You want to sit by the window?

286
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,400
Alright, okay.

287
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,670
Bus's departing!

288
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:56,940
(131 Terminus - Guli Reservoir Station)

289
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:04,830
It's your phone.

290
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,520
Answer it.

291
00:13:08,180 --> 00:13:10,700
(Liu Dong)

292
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,040
Hello.

293
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:15,790
Hello, Liu Dong...

294
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,000
Let me talk to him.

295
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,950
Liu Dong,

296
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:25,230
why are you calling your uncle again?

297
00:13:29,150 --> 00:13:30,320
Buying a burial plot, huh?

298
00:13:35,422 --> 00:13:36,800
Liu Dong, listen to me carefully.

299
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:39,680
I'll make this crystal clear.

300
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:41,440
We are absolutely

301
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,920
not buying a burial plot.

302
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,230
If your family ancestors
have a problem with that,

303
00:13:47,355 --> 00:13:49,133
they can come talk to me themselves.

304
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,280
Otherwise, they better
just rest in peace.

305
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,750
They're dead.

306
00:13:53,750 --> 00:13:55,320
What else do they want?

307
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,240
Bye!

308
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:01,750
I think he's got our message now.

309
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:06,750
Take it back.

310
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,920
Liu Debao!

311
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:14,333
Why did you do that, Liu Debao?

312
00:14:14,355 --> 00:14:15,750
Why did you throw the phone out?

313
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,560
Sir, please pull over!

314
00:14:17,870 --> 00:14:19,470
- Sir!
- I can't pull over here.

315
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:21,710
My phone...

316
00:14:21,733 --> 00:14:23,030
If you don't pull over, I'm going

317
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:23,950
to jump out the window.

318
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,360
I had to say something like that

319
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,560
just to get you open the door.

320
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,670
Unbelievable.

321
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,200
Liu Debao,

322
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,120
get out!

323
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,600
Why are you still sitting there?

324
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,710
Come on!

325
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,230
Liu Debao, get out!

326
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,440
Stop the bus!

327
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:50,710
Stop it!

328
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,120
Liu Debao!

329
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,910
This song, "Farewell",

330
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:56,590
has a touch of sadness to it.

331
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,480
So when you're performing,

332
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,160
try not to smile too much.

333
00:15:00,390 --> 00:15:01,310
For the first line...

334
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:05,400
♪By the old road♪

335
00:15:06,070 --> 00:15:07,000
Lower the wrists.

336
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:11,630
