stretches to the sky♪

337
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,750
As your hands come down...

338
00:15:14,270 --> 00:15:17,600
♪The evening breeze brushes the willows♪

339
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:20,155
Let your body follow naturally.

340
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:28,230
♪The sun sets beyond the hills♪

341
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:33,560
♪At the edge of the sky♪

342
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:37,040
♪To the corners of the earth♪

343
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:44,000
♪Most close friends have drifted away♪

344
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:52,150
♪Moments of joy are rare in this life♪

345
00:15:52,790 --> 00:16:00,520
♪But farewells are far too many♪

346
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:02,470
Shen Qing!

347
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:13,530
♪At the edge of the sky,
to the corners of the earth♪

348
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:18,090
♪Most close friends have drifted away♪

349
00:16:18,110 --> 00:16:19,030
Found it.

350
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:28,720
♪Moments of joy are rare in this life♪

351
00:16:29,090 --> 00:16:35,210
♪But farewells are far too many♪

352
00:16:35,310 --> 00:16:36,270
I ordered you something.

353
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:37,190
Thank you.

354
00:16:45,222 --> 00:16:47,890
