Not sure if you'll like it.

355
00:16:48,110 --> 00:16:49,030
Can I open it now?

356
00:16:49,310 --> 00:16:50,230
Go ahead.

357
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,400
And there's this card.

358
00:17:02,310 --> 00:17:03,230
It's

359
00:17:03,311 --> 00:17:04,720
filled with messages from our team,

360
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,950
all wishing you

361
00:17:06,110 --> 00:17:07,030
the best.

362
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:15,420
(To the dearest Ice)

363
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,080
Thank you.

364
00:17:37,644 --> 00:17:39,000
Please thank everyone for me.

365
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,840
It's very sweet.

366
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,800
Your gift's perfect.

367
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,150
I can take it back home

368
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,222
and use it to brew
our Minnan-style kung fu tea.

369
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:54,950
That's great.

370
00:17:55,466 --> 00:17:57,560
A change of environment,
and a change of flavor.

371
00:18:11,466 --> 00:18:12,600
I've been pushing myself

372
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:13,840
too hard these years.

373
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:15,710
I'm exhausted.

374
00:18:17,622 --> 00:18:19,040
I want to go home for a while,

375
00:18:19,622 --> 00:18:20,870
and spend some time with my dad.

376
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:24,030
That's good.

377
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:25,710
That's good.

378
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,560
It's just a shame

379
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:31,688
we won't be running together anymore.

380
00:18:33,733 --> 00:18:36,088
Sure we can.
We'll run together on the fitness app.

381
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,120
Let's see who's faster.

382
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,000
I surrender now.

383
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:51,470
Come.

384
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,640
Let's clink our cups.

385
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,830
I should be heading to my gate.

386
00:19:20,088 --> 00:19:21,230
I'll walk you to security.

387
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:22,510
No need.

388
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:24,340
It's not like we'll never
see each other again.

389
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:26,320
This is far enough.

390
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:39,270
Take care.

391
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:41,600
Take care.

392
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,030
Ice.

393
00:20:07,711 --> 00:20:08,990
I don't have insomnia anymore.

394
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,150
And when I run,

395
00:20:11,355 --> 00:20:12,760
I don't think about reports or data.

396
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:14,400
I just

397
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,390
focus on my breath,

398
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:18,720
on the air,

399
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,800
and on the freedom of that moment.

400
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,190
Thank you.

401
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:19,180
(Guli Reservoir Station)

402
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,080
Sir?

403
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,360
Sir?

404
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:30,640
This is the last stop.

405
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,040
Is this the 131 terminal?

406
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,120
Yes, it is.

407
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:07,133
Finally! I've been trying
to get through to you.

408
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,920
Earlier, my husband and I

409
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:10,720
were riding your bus.

410
00:22:11,170 --> 00:22:12,030
But then

411
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:14,040
he got mad and threw
his phone out the window.

412
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:16,080
Your bus just drove off after I got off.

413
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,630
I was shouting, but you didn't stop.

414
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:20,160
My husband ended up following the bus,

415
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,480
So I'm trying to find out,
at which stop did he get off?

416
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:23,720
Are you talking

417
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:25,720
about the older guy
in the royal blue T-shirt?

418
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:26,680
Yes, that's him!

419
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,520
He rode all the way to the last stop.

420
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:29,870
He looked very distracted.

421
00:22:30,310 --> 00:22:31,240
When he got off,

422
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,577
he was walking like a lost soul.

423
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,480
Alright, got it.

424
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,430
Please stop!

425
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:42,400
Stop!

426
00:22:43,350 --> 00:22:44,760
- Thank you.
- Senior card.

427
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,230
Shuishan.

428
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,630
Lina,

429
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:52,190
can you and your dad

430
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:53,760
give Shuishan a ride home?

431
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:56,510
I didn't drive here today, Mr. Gou.

432
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:57,430
It's fine, really.

433
00:22:57,550 --> 00:22:58,470
I can go home myself.

434
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:00,910
How about I walk with you then?

435
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:04,190
It's fine. I actually feel
like going shopping.

436
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,800
You wouldn't be interested in that.

437
00:23:06,270 --> 00:23:08,480
Shan, how about I come with you?

438
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:10,170
I was thinking of
shopping for some clothes.

439
00:23:10,177 --> 00:23:11,310
- Sure!
- Okay.

440
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:12,630
Gou, I'm going with her then.

441
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,350
Don't forget about Ding.

442
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,600
- Got it.
- Bye.

443
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,960
You two can ride with me.

444
00:23:17,111 --> 00:23:18,230
We'll drop Ding off first.

445
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:19,750
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

446
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:21,070
Ding, let's go.

447
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:21,990
Okay.

448
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:31,300
(Guli Reservoir Station)

449
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:38,430
Guli Reservoir Station?

450
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,630
Sir, is your last stop

451
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,280
Guli Reservoir Station?

452
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,320
Yes.

453
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,120
Hello, mom.

454
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:06,150
Lina,

455
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,800
listen,

456
00:24:07,977 --> 00:24:09,670
I have a really bad feeling about this.

457
00:24:10,711 --> 00:24:13,022
I think something is going
to happen to your dad.

458
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:17,080
What? Where are you guys?

459
00:24:17,555 --> 00:24:18,800
I'm coming over right now.

460
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,880
Send me the location.

461
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:22,040
What's wrong, Lina?

462
00:24:22,244 --> 00:24:24,511
My mom said something was going
to happen to my dad.

463
00:24:26,030 --> 00:24:26,950
Huh?

464
00:24:27,044 --> 00:24:28,955
Did she say what was
going to happen to him?

465
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:29,880
She didn't.

466
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,560
Okay.

467
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:36,790
We've set the location.

468
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:38,066
How long till we get there?

469
00:24:38,066 --> 00:24:39,200
A little over 20 minutes.

470
00:24:39,550 --> 00:24:40,400
Go faster.

471
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,320
Okay.

472
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:55,110
He never picks up.

473
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:56,222
I've called so many times.

474
00:24:59,711 --> 00:25:02,460
Maybe Shen Qing was tied up with
something and didn't hear his phone.

475
00:25:02,466 --> 00:25:03,333
Don't worry,

476
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,790
you've got us.

477
00:25:04,790 --> 00:25:05,710
He's going to be fine.

478
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,320
Yes, don't panic.

479
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:11,760
Please drive faster.

480
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,160
Okay.

