483
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,640
Liu!

484
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:57,670
Liu!

485
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,120
Dad!

486
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,360
Dad!

487
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:05,800
Come back, Dad!

488
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,190
Dad!

489
00:26:07,350 --> 00:26:08,270
Dad!

490
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,910
Please save my dad, Mr. Gou!

491
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,960
Liu, hang in there!

492
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,910
Gou is coming to you!

493
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,400
Dad!

494
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,070
Liu!

495
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:24,720
- Gou!
- Liu!

496
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:26,790
