498
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,510
Liu!

499
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:35,430
Hang in there!

500
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,640
He got him!

501
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:40,840
Mr. Gou!

502
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,230
