- Get him back, Mr. Gou!

503
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:47,040
Hang in there!

504
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:52,000
Mr. Gou!

505
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:54,670
I need a hand!

506
00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:56,030
Dad!

507
00:26:56,650 --> 00:26:57,550
Dad!

508
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,550
Come on!

509
00:26:58,550 --> 00:26:59,470
Give me a hand!

510
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,600
Dad!

511
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,110
- Dad!
- Come on.

512
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:03,480
Come on.

513
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,360
Here.

514
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:07,600
Dad!

515
00:27:09,577 --> 00:27:10,750
Put him down on the floor.

516
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:12,270
Come, Liu.

517
00:27:12,290 --> 00:27:13,160
Spit the water out.

518
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:14,533
