- Dad...

519
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:20,080
Liu Debao!

520
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,080
Get the water out.

521
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:24,310
Yes, get it all out.

522
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:27,320
Liu Debao! Liu Debao, are you okay?

523
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,920
He's fine now.

524
00:27:30,510 --> 00:27:31,440
My dad was drowning.

525
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,590
Mr. Gou saved his life!

526
00:27:33,830 --> 00:27:35,640
You were trying to kill yourself?

527
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:36,720
What are you talking about?

528
00:27:37,311 --> 00:27:39,079
Was it really his choice to want to die?

529
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:40,733
Wasn't it you
