530
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:41,750
Liu,

531
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:42,800
you're okay now.

532
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,320
Liu Debao...

533
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:52,400
Liu Debao...

534
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,320
Get the water out.

535
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:55,400
- Pat him harder.
