00:28:01,550 --> 00:28:02,470
Ding?

539
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,400
Get back here!

540
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,080
Ding?

541
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:14,960
Stop!

542
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:16,280
Gou, be careful!

543
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,520
Let's get him

544
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,800
