545
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:20,990
Come on.

546
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:22,190
Ding!

547
00:28:22,590 --> 00:28:23,510
Ding!

548
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,350
Ding, come back!

549
00:28:26,350 --> 00:28:27,270
Gou,

550
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:28,800
don't panic.

551
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,000
He can swim.

552
00:28:30,310 --> 00:28:31,800
Just get him back.

553
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,360
Ding,

554
00:28:36,590 --> 00:28:37,590
please listen.

555
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,630
