his younger days at the academy.

564
00:29:12,155 --> 00:29:13,590
He used to be a swimming champion.

565
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,030
Ding!

566
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:19,000
Come back!

567
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:22,560
Mr. Gou! Come back!

568
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:25,080
Come back!

569
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,720
Shen and the guys are calling us!

570
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:28,080
Let's get back!

571
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,560
Come back!

572
00:29:38,733 --> 00:29:39,760
